          "text": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "type": "heading",
          "anchor": "overview"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use this action to perform an app-provided operation on a list of prims.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "When this action executes, it posts a notification for which a custom app scans to perform a specific operation.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "text": "Declaration",
